@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About - Praetorium.Bridge</PageTitle>

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
        <h1>About Praetorium.Bridge</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>What is Praetorium.Bridge?</h2>
            <p>
                Praetorium.Bridge is a session management and tool orchestration platform 
                that connects AI agents with configurable tools through the Model Context Protocol (MCP).
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Session Management</strong> - Pool and manage sessions for efficient resource usage</li>
                <li><strong>Tool Configuration</strong> - Define and configure tools for your AI agents</li>
                <li><strong>Real-time Dashboard</strong> - Monitor active sessions and activity in real-time</li>
                <li><strong>Prompt Templates</strong> - Manage system prompts for your tools</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Technology</h2>
            <p>Built with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>.NET 10</li>
                <li>Blazor Server</li>
                <li>SignalR for real-time updates</li>
                <li>Model Context Protocol (MCP)</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
